<h1>How does this work</h1>
	
<p>This application is a <a href="http://jakarta.apache.org/turbine">Turbine </a>web application. 
	The Turbine site contains some background on Turbine. However many people find it not sufficent
to get started.</p>
	
<p>Antelope aims to provide a good sample of the commonly used features of Turbine and specicially how 
	to use it with the <a href="zebra.berlios.de">Zebra</a> workflow engine.</p>
	
<h2>So what is Turbine</h2>
<p>Turbine is a web application framework which makes it easy to build web applications within a Servlet environment.</p>

